<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="resign-v">resign <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'zaɪn/    美 /rɪ'zaɪn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>辞去 (职务)；放弃：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>resign from</strong> a job 
辞职</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They overheard him say that he hoped John would resign. 
他们无意中听到他说希望约翰辞职。</p><footer>人教⑦ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Tom has resigned his membership of the golf club.
汤姆已经退出了高尔夫球俱乐部。</p></div></div>